{
  "stanzas": [
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "Seek ye first the kingdom,"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "‘Tis your Father’s will."
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "So the voice of Jesus bids us follow still."
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "Saviour, we would hear Thee,"
        },
        {
          "number": 5,
          "text": "Follow, find, and see;"
        },
        {
          "number": 6,
          "text": "And in life’s adventure Thy disciples be."
        }
      ],
      "number": 1
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "As for hidden treasure,"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "Or for matchless pearl,"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "When at last discovered,"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "some will sell their all;"
        },
        {
          "number": 5,
          "text": "So, when breaks the vision of that"
        },
        {
          "number": 6,
          "text": "kingdom fair,"
        },
        {
          "number": 7,
          "text": "Ours shall be its riches And its beauty rare."
        }
      ],
      "number": 2
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "As the silent leaven works its secret way,"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "Or as grows the seed grain"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "through the night and day;"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "Lord, so be the increase, peaceable but sure,"
        },
        {
          "number": 5,
          "text": "Of Thy word within us,"
        },
        {
          "number": 6,
          "text": "And Thy kingdom’s power."
        }
      ],
      "number": 3
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "As the tender seedling grows up"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "tall and strong,"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "And the birds of heaven to its"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "branches throng; So shall all God’s children,"
        },
        {
          "number": 5,
          "text": "from the east and west,"
        },
        {
          "number": 6,
          "text": "Gather to His kingdom, In its shadow rest."
        }
      ],
      "number": 4
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "Humblest shall be greatest,"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "poor in spirit reign;"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "Home shall come the childlike,"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "born through Thee again;"
        },
        {
          "number": 5,
          "text": "Eager hearts arrive there on the"
        },
        {
          "number": 6,
          "text": "pilgrim’s road,"
        },
        {
          "number": 7,
          "text": "Hail! The kingdom glorious of the living God!"
        }
      ],
      "number": 5
    }
  ],
  "title": "Seek Ye First the Kingdom"
}
